-- French Doctor Charged by U.S. With Tipping Hedge Funds on Drug Trials
-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 2010-11-02T16:36:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/french-doctor-charged-by-u-s-with-tipping-hedge-funds-on-drug-trials.html
A French doctor, Yves Benhamou, was
charged today by federal prosecutors with tipping off six hedge
funds on the results of drug trials. The case was filed in U.S.
district court in Manhattan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Patricia Hurtado in New York at 
